dataIdInfo.idPurp: The purpose of this GIS dataset is to indicate the extent of remedial action activities at specific waste sites using contour lines. The contour lines typically represent the excavation or stockpile areas associated with the site. The referenced drawing or CVP figure should be consulted to interpret the contour lines.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This draft dataset contains the contour lines from the post-excavation survey(s) for reclassified waste sites. The intended purpose of the dataset is for project land use planning and is limited to WCH internal use only. Since post-excavation surveys are not always performed, the data may not be available or may only be partially available for any given waste site. As a result, this dataset should by definition be considered incomplete. Current status of this dataset is under development.
